OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLargely
OL,6,Fcloudy and mild overnight, with most
OL,7,Fareas remaining dry. The best of any
OL,8,Fclearer spells likely towards the east
OL,9,Fof the region. Remaining breezy.
OL,10,
OL,11,CMonday:FA cloudy but dry start, with
OL,12,Fsunny spells developing through the
OL,13,Fmorning, the best of these in the
OL,14,Feast. Chance of a few spots of rain
OL,15,Ffurther west later. Breezy.
